data.description: Welcome to 108 Luke Dr, a charming residence nestled in the highly sought-after North Paulding School District in Dallas, GA 30132. Boasting a prime location with no HOA fees and USDA eligibility, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience.    Featuring 3 bedrooms and two baths, this property offers a versatile flex space in the basement, providing ample room for your unique lifestyle needs whether its an office, game room or even a craft room. The recent upgrades enhance the overall appeal, including brand new stainless steel appliances that bring a touch of luxury to the heart of the home.    The main living space has newer flooring, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen, a focal point of the home, showcases not only updated flooring, granite counter tops and appliances, but also boasts new updated light fixtures & ceiling fan, adding a fresh and modern aesthetic.     Discover the joy of seamless living in a residence that combines functionality in the ever popular North Paulding School District. Don't miss the opportunity to make 108 Luke Dr your new home.    Professional Pictures will be uploaded 12/10
